    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Wash. D.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Doesn't it seem wisest for you to forbid papers - (No not forbid - but ask",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "the co-operation of all papers) to keep all news of those discs out of the news",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "until you are sure just what they are & where from.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "It seems to us with all the enemies we have, even within our borders,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "it could be something far more important than may seem at first. I had 2 sons",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "in this war & another who over-did for his America - & we do want it really",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "protected from danger from now on. Enough are dead & maimed - with-out losing out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "now as it easily could be. Why have the papers carried that story if reporters",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "were made to see how much more sensible not to report - it except to the F.B.I.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "There is too much of danger ahead anyway -",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
